00:37:10,821 --> 00:37:13,283
So if you have, to the extent that you have,

772
00:37:13,664 --> 00:37:15,565
the attention to detail and the fortitude

773
00:37:15,625 --> 00:37:18,448
to go through the entire, all of your work,

774
00:37:18,568 --> 00:37:21,050
read through your stuff, play your game,

775
00:37:21,130 --> 00:37:22,531
pay attention to those narrative bugs,

