00:37:48,055 --> 00:37:51,418
exactly what you want the player to get out of it. So you're going to be like, yeah, okay,

786
00:37:51,478 --> 00:37:56,482
test, test, test, yep, it works as designed. But a lot of players are not going to follow

787
00:37:56,522 --> 00:37:57,323
your optimal path.

788
00:37:58,374 --> 00:38:01,337
and you need to follow suboptimal paths through your

789
00:38:01,377 --> 00:38:04,180
dialogues and through your stories to make sure those

790
00:38:04,260 --> 00:38:06,943
stories still make sense if followed in that way because if

