00:43:57,696 --> 00:44:00,517
So I always suggest that if you have to do a tutorial,

887
00:44:00,577 --> 00:44:04,118
either you do Half-Life 2's excellent silent tutorial,

888
00:44:04,318 --> 00:44:05,818
where they set up a lot of stuff visually,

