00:46:48,350 --> 00:46:51,633
That's a really easy thing on the narrative side to juggle,

946
00:46:51,673 --> 00:46:53,334
but yet still have a big consequence

947
00:46:53,354 --> 00:46:54,095
at the end of the game,

948
00:46:54,415 --> 00:46:56,697
in terms of what your final alignment is for your character.

949
00:46:58,118 --> 00:47:02,120
And also, like in the original design for the Tyranny RPG,

